  <brief_title>A Study to Evaluate Pneumococcal Polysaccharide Vaccine Effectiveness in Children With Type 1 Diabetes</brief_title>
  <official_title>Vaccine Effectiveness and Seroconversion to 23 Valent Pneumococcal Polysaccharide Vaccination in Children With Type 1 Diabetes</official_title>
